  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Sorcerer Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>Your family traces its heritage back to the ocean depths, whether scions of undersea empires left in the wake of nomadic sea-tribes, or the spawn of creeping ichthyic infiltrators into remote seaside villages. The song of the sea hums in your blood, calling the waves and all those within to your command.</p><p><b>Class Skill: </b>Swim.</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>hydraulic push (3rd), slipsream (5th), aqueous orb (7th), geyser (9th), control water (11th), beast shape IV (13th), summon monster VII (15th), seamantle (17th), world wave (19th).</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Athletic, Brew Potion, Defensive Combat Training, Dodge, Mobility, Silent Spell, Skill Focus (Swim), Toughness.</p><p><b>Bloodline Arcana: </b>Whenever you cast a spell of the water type, your effective caster level is increased by one, and summoned creatures with a swim speed or the aquatic or water type gain a +1 morale bonus on attack and damage rolls.</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>Your seaborn magical talents awaken changes in you, both mystical and physical, as you develop your powers.</p>",
